content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #86063 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

Hmm. This a is a tier-2 platform, and i128 multiplication seems to be basically entirely broken, though people are having a bit of trouble reproducing. I might tentatively suggest P-high, though P-medium might apply too? Especially if reproducing turns out to be really hard.
After looking at how tier 2 things have been prioritized in the past, I think P-medium might be a better fit, but I'm not sure.
